attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Vault"
type Vault @entity @regularPolling {
  "Unique identifier for the vault"
  id: ID!
  "The yield aggregator protocol associated with the vault"
  protocol: YieldAggregator!
  "The name of the vault"
  name: String
  "The symbol representing the vault"
  symbol: String
  "The token used as input for the vault"
  inputToken: Token!
  "The token produced as output by the vault"
  outputToken: Token
  "Tokens rewarded to users of the vault"
  rewardTokens: [RewardToken!]
  "The maximum amount that can be deposited into the vault"
  depositLimit: BigInt!
  "The fees associated with the vault"
  fees: [VaultFee!]!
  "The timestamp when the vault was created"
  createdTimestamp: BigInt!
  "The block number when the vault was created"
  createdBlockNumber: BigInt!
  "The total value locked in the vault, measured in USD"
  totalValueLockedUSD: BigDecimal!
  "The cumulative revenue from the supply side, measured in USD"
  cumulativeSupplySideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "The cumulative revenue from the protocol side, measured in USD"
  cumulativeProtocolSideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "The total cumulative revenue, measured in USD"
  cumulativeTotalRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "The balance of the input token in the vault"
  inputTokenBalance: BigInt!
  "The supply of the output token"
  outputTokenSupply: BigInt
  "The price of the output token, measured in USD"
  outputTokenPriceUSD: BigDecimal
  "The price per share of the vault"
  pricePerShare: BigDecimal
  "The amount of output tokens staked"
  stakedOutputTokenAmount: BigInt
  "The amount of emissions for reward tokens"
  rewardTokenEmissionsAmount: [BigInt!]
  "The emissions of reward tokens, measured in USD"
  rewardTokenEmissionsUSD: [BigDecimal!]
  "Daily snapshots of the vault's state"
  dailySnapshots: [VaultDailySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "vault")
  "Hourly snapshots of the vault's state"
  hourlySnapshots: [VaultHourlySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "vault")
  "Records of deposits made into the vault"
  deposits: [Deposit!]! @derivedFrom(field: "vault")
  "Records of withdrawals from the vault"
  withdraws: [Withdraw!]! @derivedFrom(field: "vault")
  "The first token in a pair, used internally"
  _token0: Token!
  "The second token in a pair, used internally"
  _token1: Token!
  "The amount of the first token"
  _token0Amount: BigInt!
  "The amount of the second token"
  _token1Amount: BigInt!
  "The USD value of the first token amount"
  _token0AmountUSD: BigDecimal!
  "The USD value of the second token amount"
  _token1AmountUSD: BigDecimal!
}"}
